title: Suspicious Eventlog Clear
id: 27b5f8bc-38ab-4958-8db5-4ed303ca90b4
related:
    - id: 0f017df3-8f5a-414f-ad6b-24aff1128278
      type: derived
status: experimental
description: Detects usage of known powershell cmdlets to clear the Windows event logs.
references:
    - https://twitter.com/oroneequalsone/status/1568432028361830402
    - https://github.com/redcanaryco/atomic-red-team/blob/f339e7da7d05f6057fdfcdd3742bfcf365fee2a9/atomics/T1070.001/T1070.001.md
    - https://eqllib.readthedocs.io/en/latest/analytics/5b223758-07d6-4100-9e11-238cfdd0fe97.html
author: Tyler Casey @1qazCasey, @scythe_io
date: 2024-04-24
tags:
    - attack.defense_evasion
    - attack.t1070.001
logsource:
    product: windows
    category: proc_creation
detection:
    selection:
        CommandLine|contains:
            - 'Clear-EventLog '
            - 'Remove-EventLog '
            - 'Limit-EventLog '
            - 'Clear-WinEvent '
    condition: selection
falsepositives:
    - Unknown.
level: high
